Establish a policy for the generation of revenue from saleable recyclables and include the same in the Municipal Revenue Code;

Review and update its 10-year SWM Plan and prepare a comprehensive work and financial plan relative to solid waste management operations to establish the timing and extent of implementation of each program, project and activities during the year, and to employ monitoring mechanisms to ensure full implementation thereof.

