We recommended and the management agreed that:
The Local Chief Executive requires the Inventory Committee to prepare and submit the RCPPE in the required format;
The Municipal Accountant and the GSO reconcile their respective accounting and property records;
The Municipal Accountant and GSO maintain the required PPE Ledger Cards and Property Cards respectively; and
